## Tests rapides

```bash
# Récupérer un shortcode actif
docker exec creazot-ulm-php-1 bin/console dbal:run-sql \
  "SELECT public_shortcode FROM reservation WHERE public_shortcode IS NOT NULL ORDER BY debut DESC LIMIT 1"

# Test API JSON
curl -H "Accept: application/json" "https://logic-ciel.com/r/<shortcode>"

# Test page HTML SSR
curl -H "Accept: text/html" "https://logic-ciel.com/r/<shortcode>"
```
